{"tid":2024341,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【明撐快必譚得志】大家投票支持佢贏九東初選","createTime":"2020-05-19T14:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T14:21:37.000Z","uid":175314,"like":13,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"08438188386571f92b5afc1044851a95928bc754","tid":2024341,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"2020年9月立法會選舉，35+許勝不許敗，民主陣營決定全香港5區初選，選出5區的參選隊伍，其餘候選人就一定要選前棄選，同埋幫助其他民主陣營過票+拉票，減低因為互相界票而令到 35+ 失敗。<br />\n<br />\n初選之前想做一下民調，以下嘅潛在候選人，大家覺得邊個會勝出初選呢？<br />\n<br />\n投票規則：每人只可以投1票，投票後不能更改，投票需要登入Gmail，但不會記名。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家廣傳俾你地啲朋友/家人 FB, WhatsApp 群組，幫手投一票!!!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScH2pHfvzQHq-cjcV84ZVdYbWCFxhBwjn_vSFzGrIsgJCci5A/alreadyresponded\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScH2pHfvzQHq-cjcV84ZVdYbWCFxhBwjn_vSFzGrIsgJCci5A%2Falreadyresponded&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7tagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=57361afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScH2pHfvzQHq-cjcV84ZVdYbWCFxhBwjn_vSFzGrIsgJCci5A/alreadyresponded</a><br />\n<br />\n#立法會 #立法會選舉 #區議員 #區議會<br />\n立法會 立法會選舉 區議員 區議會<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">人民力量同快必一直都係支持泛民初選！<br />\n<br />\n快必譚得志喺2016年九龍東立法會選舉高票落敗，但呢四年以嚟喺九東即係觀塘、藍田、黃大仙、樂富一直攪抗爭街站，最近黑警港共問答俾街坊贏口罩，係睇得到嘅抗爭努力！ <br />\n<br />\n請支持佢贏呢一次民調初選！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同慢必陳志全一齊入立法會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：你地可以話我係打手，我費撚事澄清，我係九東撚支持譚得志！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a9745d97246df22fbcd96ce11af5184510638d","tid":2024341,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"問心 大家想唔想香港獨立建國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2024303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2024303<